subject: Adjustment Charges Paid or Payable Under the Storage of Goods Regulations for the 2019–2020 to 2025–2026 Fiscal Years Remission Order
precis: Adjustment Charges Paid or Payable Under the Storage of Goods Regulations for the 2019–2020 to 2025–2026 Fiscal Years Remission Order in order to remit any outstanding debts resulting from non-collection of inflation-based adjustments to certain fees charged by the Canada Border Services Agency between April 1, 2019 and March 31, 2026.
